  "instructions": [
    "Trim ends of Brussels sprouts and cut in half.",
    "Bring salted water to a boil; blanch sprouts for 3 minutes.",
    "Drain sprouts and shock in ice water to stop cooking; drain again.",
    "Whisk together olive oil, minced garlic, anchovy paste, lemon juice, salt, pepper, and parsley.",
    "Toss the blanched sprouts with the vinaigrette until evenly coated.",
    "Let the salad rest for 5 minutes to meld flavors.",
    "Plate the sprouts on a chilled platter.",
    "Garnish with extra parsley and serve."
